pullRequest.title: remove updating rotating dependencies and handle network error
pullRequest.bodyText:
Fix script of  updating Spring dependencies for:

Handle network errors when trying to open pom.xml instead of being interrupted.
Avoid repeating updating rotating dependencies.

Besides, due to that Spring team only supports the third party dependencies for Spring Boot's and Spring Cloud's Minor releases, thus to avoid conflicts between SDK and Spring, we hope that when SDK developers want to modify Spring-related libraries(recorded in sdk/spring/scripts/spring_managed_external_dependencies.txt), they could notice and discuss with us.

commit.message: remove updating rotating dependencies and handle network error

nodes.bodyText:
# To avoid dependency conflicts between SDK and Spring, when modify or add dependencies,
# make sure the version is same to sdk/spring/scripts/spring_managed_external_dependencies.txt.
# If your version is different from sdk/spring/scripts/spring_managed_external_dependencies.txt, 
# please discuss with Spring Integration team members:
# @chenrujun (rujche), @saragluna (xiada), @yiliuTo (yiliu6), @backwind1233 (zhihaoguo).  
# Thanks.
